=Score and qualify this inbound lead.

**Lead:** {{ $json.lead_name }}
**Email:** {{ $json.lead_email }}
**Company:** {{ $json.company_name }}
**Title:** {{ $json.title }}
**Message:** {{ $json.message }}
**Industry:** {{ $json.industry }}
**Employee Count:** {{ $json.employee_count }}
**Estimated ARR:** {{ $json.estimated_arr }}
**Funding:** {{ $json.funding_stage }}

Respond with JSON: { fit_score (0-100), tier (Hot/Warm/Cool/Not a Fit), icp_match (Strong/Partial/Weak), reason (1-2 sentences), recommended_action (specific next step), response_draft (email reply appropriate for the tier), research_notes (key things to know before a call) }

